"First light in a park."
Series: 01.

A scene from my 'morning walk' .

City Park located in the heart of Kediri City.

This photo is one of my themed up project, Liminal Spaces.

I use a mirrorless camera Fujifilm X-T20 with Fujinon Xf 35mm F2 for this project.
I usually shoot film and digital, just wait I'll reveal my works soon.
